Root Directory:
README.md (Provides context for the repository)
.env.example (Shows required environment variables for setup)
.gitignore (Crucial - excludes node_modules, .env, build outputs, etc.)
backend Directory:
backend/package.json (Dependencies and start script for Render)
backend/src/auth.js
backend/src/index.js
backend/.gitignore (Excludes node_modules, .env)
backend/render.yaml (Correction: Render uses render.yaml, not render.json for blueprint config)
frontend Directory:
frontend/package.json (Dependencies and build/start scripts for Vercel)
frontend/next.config.mjs
frontend/postcss.config.mjs
frontend/tailwind.config.ts
frontend/tsconfig.json
frontend/src/app/... (All files within app)
frontend/src/components/... (All files within components)
frontend/src/lib/... (All files within lib)
frontend/public/... (Any static assets)
frontend/.gitignore (Excludes node_modules, .next, .env.local)
frontend/vercel.json (Optional, but good for specific Vercel settings)
